{"tid":463673,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"瑪奇係唔係歷史上最好玩既線上遊戲","createTime":"2017-11-09T17:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T17:38:46.000Z","uid":128761,"like":42,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"543c4118247b28cf41f6288b49b5372c8fd54843","tid":463673,"uid":128761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:15:06.000Z","msg":"由第一次玩到依家已經10年<br />\n真心覺得到今時今日都完全冇線上遊戲可以超越到瑪奇<br />\n老實講瑪奇最正既地方係細節位<br />\n染色系統、獨立有個性既NPC、戰鬥系統，都係今時今日大把遊戲都未有<br />\n係未出細工之前平衡度又係好痴線<br />\n老手可以唔小心比隻廢怪打死、新手可以因為技術好0傷打高級地下城<br />\n<br />\n不得不說雖然係主打生活，但係瑪奇打怪既打擊感同真實度都係冇遊戲比得上<br />\n大把遊戲到今時今日打怪都係砍菜咁<br />\n但瑪奇有硬直、有打暈有打飛既動物，節奏感強、打擊感強<br />\n剩係唔同動物有唔同步行速度已經夠痴線<br />\n<br />\n就算依家已經冇玩<br />\n但瑪奇既記憶真係一世<br />\n雖然好多人覺得影任之前先係最好玩<br />\n但唔可以否認既係，係半神化出個期人流人氣都係最高峰<br />\n個種感動真係痴左線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到今時今日d所謂主打自由既遊戲真係瑪奇G1既內容都未必比得上<br />\n不過亦係玩瑪奇最大既缺點 - 好多遊戲好快就唔想再玩<br />\n所謂黑X沙漠玩左一星期就DEL左<br />\n以前玩得比較耐既魔獸、完美世界都好快玩到悶<br />\n更唔好講大把無聊低能冇深度既遊戲"},{"pid":"bbc32f1c629fc458164288d2a0c48636c6ab0605","tid":463673,"uid":79581,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:18:36.000Z","msg":"RO先係"},{"pid":"452f72e29acc03aa78a0039a7555e42418f8daf0","tid":463673,"uid":51114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:20:09.000Z","msg":"勇"},{"pid":"caac9e5862afb829bc467c917d8cdac8769bce84","tid":463673,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:31:59.000Z","msg":"係 唔明以前點解可以玩到三萬個鐘上線時間出黎<br />\n朝早九點玩到夜晚十二點，暑假日日係咁玩"},{"pid":"0552bf2cccd7e1216ff745794eb77da3696542c3","tid":463673,"uid":142822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:39:23.000Z","msg":"wow????"},{"pid":"530473900db777f48b65279d30d0f721fa8fbcd8","tid":463673,"uid":10509,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:48:37.000Z","msg":"魔力寶貝先係"},{"pid":"010581c21e9d5b36f89840f0f5b0d3648f7ca5cb","tid":463673,"uid":11081,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:53:20.000Z","msg":"以前d雲起game屌打瑪奇啦"},{"pid":"ed0415f2c325b0be160283a18833a86777a5f756","tid":463673,"uid":51566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T18:00:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魔力寶貝先係</blockquote><br />\nagree"},{"pid":"c9ec1d2c49be7b23d414868f12fae5e8b196e54a","tid":463673,"uid":18200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:44:17.000Z","msg":"Wow 瑪奇 真係好難選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7ebd0e798e7784e95af72f50919cff5a559881","tid":463673,"uid":103497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:49:31.000Z","msg":"wow先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9ad6b2dc6c940347087386832da26b16ea077d","tid":463673,"uid":39729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:41:51.000Z","msg":"魔獸世界啦"},{"pid":"c8ad4eed0e9235f7d400c9e516d64613cffc2a40","tid":463673,"uid":52525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"瑪奇同魔獸真係好難揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1890e0d203648e010b344d739f54f731f64944","tid":463673,"uid":60720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"每年一post"},{"pid":"785635898feb88d53ed96a3eab1dd8939849c7b5","tid":463673,"uid":83133,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:59:35.000Z","msg":"瑪奇係好玩嘅 <br />\n除左戰爭 生活技能都有排玩 主線故事又好睇 <br />\n仲記得以前期期出抽蛋 <br />\n搶閘12點做頭一批抽蛋高機率出正野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但出埋細緻工匠真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45b93b2a5a159fe393a535a3496c7563a3894a7","tid":463673,"uid":52062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"未轉戰鬥模式之前係<br />\n影任開始衰落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e86eba55b26e46f4bdaac70ecd9b3a3911ab8c","tid":463673,"uid":8721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:26:42.000Z","msg":"而家嘅遊戲可玩性的確無以前咁高，但其實決定一隻game好玩與否 係睇你當時用咩心態去玩<br />\n<br />\n過多五六七年 又會有其他後生仔吹奏邊隻邊隻game 係史上最乜乜乜 <br />\n<br />\n無憂無慮打機嘅時間已經唔存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係出返去做野先"},{"pid":"09985813d64c7bd58b8738532a9cd7960088badd","tid":463673,"uid":39693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:34:25.000Z","msg":"奶油手不了，負皮上一頁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我都好掛住以前啲好友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a621ca19d5bcf5322a7009afcb73c856d05eeb5c","tid":463673,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:35:25.000Z","msg":"WOW好玩好多"},{"pid":"cc67eb36b35d9a87bfee3a537b906aa488ac839c","tid":463673,"uid":155256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"好懷念 第一次玩瑪奇仲係小學時期 成家人連埋老豆都一齊玩同一個account <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前真係玩得好認真 我老豆從來都冇課過金 但佢打到起碼全server 頭二三十位都有 真係有十年了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb156b7c7e039b04c5ac01fb0fe8b0ce6e9dd76d","tid":463673,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"未至於係史上既<br />\n<br />\n好懷念"},{"pid":"3e6b8778864a3a40ee0dace84203df35c4d597a7","tid":463673,"uid":155256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"打過唔算好多online game 但佢既戰鬥模式真係睇策略, 禁制既timing 等 而唔係好似其他game 一味篤篤篤篤咁打"},{"pid":"d607f2dbd255fb1150a237d263bd5aa95af50813","tid":463673,"uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:32:33.000Z","msg":"初期真係幾好<br />\n戰鬥用技術搭救，靠裝都勁唔得去邊<br />\n一死扣耐久都好dum春唔會亂黎<br />\n圍毆更加唔得，實有人死<br />\n之後裝埋聖騎1日1次變身，有得爆下seed<br />\n補多小小能力差距唔洗卡死係升技能<br />\n冇職業，當時戰鬥見人3修都當神咁拜<br />\n特別係有埋火球，風箭之類既痴線佬<br />\n<br />\n最出名係果實魔人，食到過千敏<br />\n有耐性真係乜都得<br />\n齋玩生活做兼職賣下聖水，礦碎，羊毛/其他加工品都夠賺好多"},{"pid":"4ca69d4a925069a68a86d1fe246e52b0d59f4ba8","tid":463673,"uid":155925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>魔力寶貝先係</blockquote><br />\nagree</blockquote><br />\nAgger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91638e29d6790f68a1d4cfba75cfd4d2006eb06c","tid":463673,"uid":79137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"好玩（x）<br />\n襟玩（o)"},{"pid":"419ec1be6f2e18ec951cb744b87b8eebe6e987c8","tid":463673,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:40:34.000Z","msg":"G1-G3 好玩，出左精靈巨人之後差左啲<br />\n故事膨脹得太快"}]}